folder: Sheepshead Bay Road & Voorhies Avenue, Brooklyn, NY
original_title: Brooklyn: Sheepshead Bay Road - Voorhies Avenue
text:
(1)
Sheepshead Bay Road, north of Voorhies Ave., showing at the left, property belonging to A. Soeller (1890) and in the background is the Island View Hotel (1890) known by its cupola, and to the right of it is the home of C.F. O'Neil. The collector and photographer states the Island View Hotel to be the hotel of William Schuessler.

December 1923.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

(2)
The same, showing a close-up of the Island View Hotel at the N.E. corner of East 16th Street. Sheepshead Bay Road turns left at this point and forms a sharp angle.
1922.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
